Field Detail

OVERRIDE_HARDWARE_ACCELERATION_TO

public static final String OVERRIDE_HARDWARE_ACCELERATION_TO
This key is used when adaptor must override the view's hardware acceleration flag by using the value provided. If null returned, no action should be performed to a view. If a value under the key is false, View.LAYER_TYPE_SOFTWARE should be applied, View.LAYER_TYPE_HARDWARE otherwise.
